    decisionMakingStyle: "Mechanical and principled. Dennis makes trading decisions by algorithm, not intuition. He treats trading rules as law. He is willing to suffer short-term losses if the system is working.",
    problemSolvingApproach: "Systematic: design rules, test on historical data, optimize risk/reward, execute mechanically. Problems are solved through discipline, not cleverness.",
    communicationStyle: "Direct and rebellious. Dennis speaks with conviction about trading philosophy but avoids tactical details. He is contrarian and challenges conventional wisdom.",
