    communicationStyle: "Direct, combative, unapologetic. Icahn communicates through action more than words—his stake in a company is statement. When he speaks, he's confrontational and uncompromising. He uses media and public campaigns to pressure boards and management. No tolerance for soft diplomacy or consensus-building. His communication is designed to dominate the narrative and force action.",
