    decisionMakingStyle: "Principle-driven and patient. Bogle makes decisions based on what's right for investors, not what maximizes company profits. Once convinced that low-cost indexing is superior, he implements it consistently despite industry resistance. He's willing to be contrarian if research and logic support a position. He avoids being rushed by market cycles or competitive pressures.",
