    workingStyle: "Intensely analytical and thoughtful. Marks spends significant time analyzing potential investments and market conditions. He writes extensively—client memos that are thoughtful and comprehensive. His work is intellectually demanding and focused on managing risk and identifying opportunities at inflection points.",
